(5, 1, '2014-08-09 02:13:58', '2014-08-09 02:13:58', '<h4>Why we’re the Best!</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We use Enzyme Technology. We only use 100% all-natural, non-toxic, non-corrosive, non-hazardous, non-flammable and a Neutral pH solution.</li>\r\n	<li>We conduct an On-site inspection resulting in a Written Report of your needs and expectations.</li>\r\n	<li>Individual Contract outlining the details of the job and the time frame for its completion.</li>\r\n	<li>We take note of any requirements that are specific to your Individual Situation.</li>\r\n	<li>Our Professional Staff are “Police Check” Certified as reliable trustworthy workers.</li>\r\n	<li>Our Services are fully insured.</li>\r\n	<li>We use environment-friendly products. We’ll have your premises “Spic-And-Span” in record time.</li>\r\n	<li>We have a team of fully qualified individuals.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Safety First</h4>\r\nOur highly trained staff is concerned with your safety and that of your business.  We use a completely safe, non-toxic cleaning solutions. We ensure that all appropriate measures are taken in every circumstance to maintain the highest level of safety and security possible.\r\n<h4>Our Know-How</h4>\r\nOur professionally trained staff uses the latest equipment, latest techniques and an All-Natural Cleaning solution to ensure that your cleaning experience is <strong><em>“Top-Of-the-Line”</em></strong> in every possible way. Whether you need windows cleaned, floors washed and waxed, or restrooms sanitized, we are up for the task.\r\n\r\nOur staff is personally trained and tested by our owner and founder, Thomas O’Shannassy, which ensures the highest quality workmanship and expertise possible.\r\n<h4>We Specialise</h4>\r\nNo matter what the job, or the circumstances, we can surpass your cleaning needs.\r\n\r\nOur highly trained staff will clean anything from ovens, to upholstery. We have specialised Cleaning Equipment for every cleaning job and the knowledge and expertise to use it!\r\n<h4>You Are the Motivation</h4>\r\nWe are interested in you, your business, building and an on-going relationship with you; so our staff would like to get to know your situation and your needs – today, tomorrow and next week.  We want to be Partners with you, not just, ‘the cleaning company’, but someone you can get to know and trust! The success of your business is as important to us as it is to you, because clean, safe, partners are good business; and good business is what we do.\r\n<h4>We are here for the Long Haul</h4>\r\n<em><strong>Enzymatic</strong></em> is here to stay.  We’ve put down roots in the community and we’re a growing business. We’ve provided outstanding service to many customers over the years and plan to continue doing so for years to come.  You can be sure that when that emergency happens or some special unexpected circumstances requires our services, we’ll be there to do what’s needed in a fast and efficient manner. Our Professional Team, Support Staff and everyone at <em><strong>Enzymatic</strong></em> is here to serve and work with you.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2014-08-10 10:40:09', '2014-08-10 10:40:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost/enzymatic/?page_id=5', 0, 'page', '', 0),
