(91, 1, '2014-08-09 12:13:47', '2014-08-09 12:13:47', '<strong>Hashirama</strong> was born as the oldest of four children to Butsuma, leader of the Senju clan. As a child during the Warring States Period, Hashirama first came across Madara Uchiha at the edge of a river where the young Uchiha was attempting to skip a stone all the way across. Easily getting a rock to the other side, Hashirama introduced himself to Madara as his rival in stone skipping, and noted that he was clearly leading.[3] Neither Hashirama nor Madara revealed their surnames, as it was unwise in such an era.', 'Hashirama Senju', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'hashirama-senju', '', '', '2014-08-10 05:29:38', '2014-08-10 05:29:38', '', 0, 'http://localhost/enzymatic/?post_type=team&#038;p=91', 1, 'team', '', 0),
