(135, 1, '2014-08-10 10:41:36', '2014-08-10 10:41:36', 'The last thing you want to think about when you’re moving house is the cleaning. But if you want your bond back you’re going to have to exert some effort or save your time and energy and get someone else to do the job for you.\r\n\r\nOur End of Lease cleaners are equipped with all the necessary tools, equipment and a powerful enzyme-based cleaning solution.\r\n<h2>End of Lease Cleaning Checklist:</h2>\r\n<h4>Kitchen cleaning</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>All cupboards to be cleaned, the fronts plus inside &amp; outside</li>\r\n	<li>Fridge to be cleaned inside and out</li>\r\n	<li>Oven to be cleaned inside &amp; outside</li>\r\n	<li>Dishwasher to be cleaned inside &amp; Outside</li>\r\n	<li>Floors to be hovered and moped</li>\r\n	<li>All inside windows totally washed and doors spot cleaned</li>\r\n	<li>All skirtings to be dusted and wiped over</li>\r\n	<li>Light fittings to be dusted and or spot cleaned plus wiped clean</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Bathroom cleaning</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>All inside windows and doors to be cleaned</li>\r\n	<li>Toilet to be cleaned</li>\r\n	<li>Shower screen and floor</li>\r\n	<li>Shower head to be de scaled</li>\r\n	<li>Bath to be cleaned</li>\r\n	<li>Mirrors to be cleaned</li>\r\n	<li>Any cupboards and shelves to be cleaned</li>\r\n	<li>All skirtings to be dusted</li>\r\n	<li>Light fittings to be dusted and or wiped down</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Bedrooms</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>All inside wndows and doors to be cleaned</li>\r\n	<li>Inside of wardrobes and cupboards to be cleaned</li>\r\n	<li>Light fittings to be dusted and or wiped over</li>\r\n	<li>Full vacuum floor or carpets</li>\r\n	<li>Cleaning of mirrors</li>\r\n	<li>Cleaning of skirting boards</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Lounge</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>All Windows inside and doors to be cleaned</li>\r\n	<li>Inside of cupboards and shelving units etc</li>\r\n	<li>Light fittings to be dusted and or wiped over</li>\r\n	<li>Full vacuum floor or carpet</li>\r\n	<li>Cleaning of mirrors</li>\r\n	<li>Cleaning of skirting boards</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Hallway and stairs</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Vacuuming of stairs and hallways</li>\r\n	<li>Skirting boards to be cleaned</li>\r\n	<li>Any light fittings to be dusted and or wiped over to remove any marks</li>\r\n</ul>', 'End of Lease', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-10 10:41:36', '2014-08-10 10:41:36', '', 15, 'http://localhost/enzymatic/15-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(136, 1, '2014-08-10 10:42:16', '2014-08-10 10:42:16', '<h2>Floor Care</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h4>Carpet and Carpet Steam Cleaning</h4>\r\nVacuuming is great for day-to-day carpet maintenance but to keep it at peak performance, professional deep cleaning of carpet every 12 to 18 months is necessary.\r\n\r\nAt Enzymatic, we use an enzyme-based formula that dissolves and removes all types of stains and odours, leaves no soapy residue and we use colour-safe bleach for carpets including 5th-generation carpets.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h4>Polishing &amp; buffing all hard surfaces</h4>\r\nBeautiful floors can be one of the most impressive features of your facility. Well-maintained floors enhance your professional image and provide a clean, safe working environment.\r\n\r\nAlthough hard surface floors can be extremely durable, they require proper maintenance to preserve their resilience and luster. Our surface floor cleaning methods, floor care techniques and commercial grade floor waxes will exceed your high standards of cleanliness and floor appearance.\r\n<h4>List of Hard-Surface Floors Services:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Floor stripping and waxing</li>\r\n	<li>Floor scrubbing and refinishing</li>\r\n	<li>Floor polishing</li>\r\n	<li>Floor buffing/burnishing</li>\r\n	<li>Floor maintenance program</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Strata Maintenance', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-10 10:42:16', '2014-08-10 10:42:16', '', 17, 'http://localhost/enzymatic/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
